looks like when you are pleasing women.

23
00:02:51,480 --> 00:02:54,439
Shen Dong Yang woke me up early in the morning.

24
00:02:57,280 --> 00:03:00,160
So I'm sleepy now.
I'd like to get some sleep.

25
00:03:00,160 --> 00:03:01,720
Mr. Fu.

26
00:03:02,639 --> 00:03:04,319
Make yourself at home.

27
00:03:12,160 --> 00:03:13,759
Jiang Ying Xian!

28
00:03:24,079 --> 00:03:28,000
 What exactly does she want? 

29
00:03:37,880 --> 00:03:47,680
Cheng. This time, we must fulfill all our
vengeance, and take back what we've lost.

30
00:03:53,760 --> 00:03:56,759
I cuffed you, so you really didn't move?

31
00:04:01,880 --> 00:04:04,119
Two hours.

32
00:04:04,119 --> 00:04:05,399
You have a lot of stamina.

33
00:04:05,399 --> 00:04:07,120
Is this fun?

34
00:04:07,799 --> 00:04:11,240
Yes, it is.

35
00:04:16,160 --> 00:04:17,720
Are you angry?

36
00:04:19,640 --> 00:04:21,640
Don't give in too quickly.

37
00:04:21,640 --> 00:04:25,599
Otherwise, I'll lose the fun quickly.

38
00:04:26,372 --> 00:04:28,771
What do you want?

39
00:04:31,439 --> 00:04:33,239
What do I want?

40
00:04:34,799 --> 00:04:38,799
The disenchantment of the prodigal,
and the fall of a saint.

41
00:04:40,439 --> 00:04:42,919
Isn't that what the world loves to see?

42
00:04:46,999 --> 00:04:53,999
And I love to see the struggles of humanity,

43
00:04:55,320 --> 00:05:01,440
especially that of somebody like you
who seems nobler than me.

44
00:05:08,879 --> 00:05:10,320
Hold me.

45
00:05:17,799 --> 00:05:19,559
Come and hold me.

46
00:05:30,130 --> 00:05:32,576
 ♫ The picture's yellowed ♫ 

47
00:05:33,640 --> 00:05:35,559
 ♫ But it can't dim ♫ 

48
00:05:35,559 --> 00:05:37,525
Take me to the bathroom.

49
00:05:43,720 --> 00:05:49,146
 ♫ It's like a handbook of memories ♫ 

50
00:05:49,146 --> 00:05:56,478
 ♫ Of what we've done ♫ 

51
00:05:57,600 --> 00:06:00,168
 ♫ The glass is tinkling ♫ 

52
00:06:01,001 --> 00:06:03,565
 ♫ You got an unnatural look ♫ 

53
00:06:03,565 --> 00:06:08,835
 ♫ Of panic on your face ♫ 

54
