58
00:06:31,834 --> 00:06:33,511
 ♫ I'll stop ♫ 

59
00:06:33,511 --> 00:06:41,256
 ♫ And tear down my pretense of modesty. ♫ 

60
00:06:44,799 --> 00:06:46,978
 Does he really think I feel cold? 

61
00:06:49,129 --> 00:06:55,867
 ♫ I'm glad I can love and hate you ♫ 

62
00:06:55,867 --> 00:06:59,913
 ♫ I kiss you softly amidst the prosperousness ♫ 

63
00:07:00,520 --> 00:07:04,239
I usually put a little rose petal in the bathtub.

64
00:07:07,840 --> 00:07:09,919
