65
00:07:11,439 --> 00:07:15,640
You know there are always men
who pester me and send me flowers.

66
00:07:15,640 --> 00:07:18,174
This is what Shen Dong Yang gave you earlier,
isn't it?

67
00:07:23,204 --> 00:07:26,640
 ♫ You and I are humming softly ♫ 

68
00:07:26,640 --> 00:07:30,907
 ♫ We can't let such a nice night go by ♫ 

69
00:07:30,907 --> 00:07:34,279
 ♫ After tonight, we'll be gone ♫ 

70
00:07:34,279 --> 00:07:41,113
 ♫ And on our own ♫ 

71
00:07:42,136 --> 00:07:45,486
 ♫ Drifting aimlessly ♫ 

72
00:07:45,486 --> 00:07:48,636
 ♫ Not knowing where to go ♫ 

73
00:07:50,199 --> 00:07:51,986
The water's hot.

74
00:07:55,706 --> 00:07:59,126
 ♫ I stand alone against it ♫ 

75
00:07:59,126 --> 00:08:01,326
 ♫ But I don't want to ♫ 

76
00:08:01,326 --> 00:08:07,896
 ♫ The longing catches me off guard ♫ 

77
00:08:09,436 --> 00:08:15,326
