78
00:08:16,406 --> 00:08:17,906
 ♫ Tossing and turning, lost in confusion ♫ 

79
00:08:17,906 --> 00:08:26,896
 ♫ In the darkness, I lose my way ♫ 

80
00:08:37,439 --> 00:08:39,200
Take me to bed.

81
00:08:44,170 --> 00:08:51,083
 ♫ The music plays in the city's churches ♫ 

82
00:08:51,083 --> 00:08:57,387
 ♫ I should've been with you forever ♫ 

83
00:08:57,387 --> 00:09:00,998
 ♫ But it can't last when there's chaos ♫ 

84
00:09:00,998 --> 00:09:04,799
 ♫ And when I look back,
there is just rubble and empty alleys ♫ 

85
