Turn off the light. I need to sleep.

89
00:09:44,319 --> 00:09:50,560
 If he's really Jiang Ying Si,
will he fall in love with his half-sister? 

90
00:10:04,559 --> 00:10:08,920
Boss. At Jiangbei Village,
we expect to open next month.

91
00:10:10,000 --> 00:10:11,439
