92
00:10:11,439 --> 00:10:14,680
Mr. Shen was really helpful this time.

93
00:10:17,000 --> 00:10:19,040
Indeed.

94
00:10:21,199 --> 00:10:23,120
 As long as you're willing to help in this matter, 

95
00:10:23,120 --> 00:10:26,920
 I'll give you 10% of the profit
from your shipment through Jiang's Dock. 

96
00:10:26,920 --> 00:10:28,319
Ying Xian.

97
00:10:28,319 --> 00:10:34,560
Based on our relationship,
even without this 10%, I will definitely help you.

98
00:10:37,120 --> 00:10:39,760
Even if you borrow Master Shen's connections,

99
00:10:39,760 --> 00:10:42,400
 you still need to pay someone to handle it, 

100
00:10:42,400 --> 00:10:46,280
 so no matter how,
I can't let you lose out on that, right? 

101
00:10:46,280 --> 00:10:51,479
Besides, how can friendship be stronger
than a relationship of interest?

102
00:10:53,160 --> 00:10:57,479
I'm sure I'll make a solid profit
doing business with you.

103
00:10:57,479 --> 00:10:59,520
As long as you're willing to help.

104
00:10:59,520 --> 00:11:02,440
Okay.
I'll give you an answer in a few days.

105
00:11:03,240 --> 00:11:05,040
Stop.

106
00:11:05,040 --> 00:11:07,160
 Stop what? 

107
00:11:07,160 --> 00:11:09,079
 I just want you to have fun. 

108
00:11:09,079 --> 00:11:10,639
 Are you happy? 

109
00:11:11,959 --> 00:11:15,639
I won't spoil your fun.
I'll wait for your message.

110
00:11:22,160 --> 00:11:24,320
