111
00:11:25,880 --> 00:11:28,239
Jiang Ying Xian is jealous?

112
00:11:33,719 --> 00:11:35,560
How can that be?

113
00:11:39,400 --> 00:11:41,001
Dong Yang.

114
00:11:47,980 --> 00:11:50,520
Come on. Put it on.

115
00:11:50,520 --> 00:11:52,720
I'll stay here tonight.

116
00:12:08,559 --> 00:12:12,880
I used to think you always gave me new clothes
because you liked me,

117
00:12:12,880 --> 00:12:16,440
but I didn't realize you just wanted me
to dress up like her to please you.

118
00:12:16,440 --> 00:12:18,240
You jerk!

119
00:12:22,280 --> 00:12:24,239
Uninhibited.

120
00:12:31,719 --> 00:12:33,639
Shen Dong Yang!

121
00:12:39,160 --> 00:12:44,199
By the way, keep an eye on what Jiang Ying Qi
is doing these days.

122
00:12:44,199 --> 00:12:47,160
He's been weirdly quiet these days.

123
00:12:47,160 --> 00:12:50,999
Mr. Ying Qi seems to be
at the Dance Hall all the time lately.

124
00:12:53,000 --> 00:12:55,519
He may be up to some tricks again.

125
00:12:56,719 --> 00:12:59,760
Any news from the North?

126
00:12:59,760 --> 00:13:02,840
It's been too long, so there's no clue.

127
00:13:06,280 --> 00:13:08,680
Then keep investigating Fu Cheng.

128
00:13:09,360 --> 00:13:14,319
Boss, don't forget how your brother
ended up in this position.

129
00:13:14,319 --> 00:13:21,839
He's the eldest son, educated enough, competent,
ten years older than you, and a worthy successor,

130
00:13:21,839 --> 00:13:24,199
but he made such a mistake with his marriage

131
00:13:24,199 --> 00:13:27,520
that he insisted on marrying
a female performer with a bad reputation.

132
00:13:27,520 --> 00:13:30,240
Master was so angry
he didn't even show up on the wedding day.

133
00:13:30,240 --> 00:13:31,720
I know.

134
00:13:33,439 --> 00:13:35,559
It's because of my brother's falling out
with my father

135
00:13:35,559 --> 00:13:39,960
