world that I've been given this opportunity.

136
00:13:41,000 --> 00:13:42,959
Don't worry.

137
00:13:42,959 --> 00:13:45,370
I'm not a playgirl.

138
00:13:45,370 --> 00:13:48,810
Some things can only be a pastime.

139
