was in charge of.

143
00:14:08,479 --> 00:14:13,399
Now she takes care of most
of the important business of the Jiang family.

144
00:14:17,719 --> 00:14:21,639
She is a strange person.

145
00:14:23,280 --> 00:14:27,400
She is not only thoughtful
but also so unpredictable

146
00:14:27,400 --> 00:14:31,559
that it's hard,
for people to figure out what she's up to.

147
00:14:31,559 --> 00:14:35,439
We should be careful with this woman,

148
00:14:35,439 --> 00:14:39,839
but if we succeed,
the whole Jiang family will be in our hands.

149
00:14:39,839 --> 00:14:47,080
But I always felt that she was testing me
rather than being interested in me.

150
00:14:51,880 --> 00:14:53,720
I don't know...

151
00:14:56,400 --> 00:14:59,320
which one of us is the prey in the end.

152
00:15:02,764 --> 00:15:08,959
My brother is disobedient, and married to
a woman from a family that doesn't match ours,

153
00:15:08,959 --> 00:15:12,079
